    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to people who have withdrawn from the world by living on top of high columns or pillars, particularly the early Christian ascetics.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
